21:18.377 --> 21:20.880
<i>Grantham is believed
to have died in the explosion...</i>

21:21.088 --> 21:23.762
<i>with crew members
whose names are being held...</i>

21:23.966 --> 21:25.468
Come on.
There's gotta be more!

21:25.676 --> 21:28.646
The coroner's looking at
what's left of Grantham.

21:28.846 --> 21:32.521
It's like the Norman case. There
wasn't enough left to put on a pizza.

21:32.725 --> 21:35.854
- What evidence connects the deaths?
- Am I hearing correctly?

21:36.061 --> 21:38.814
Is the one-man army
really asking for help?

21:39.023 --> 21:41.151
- Jackson, call for you!
- Who is it?

21:41.358 --> 21:43.235
Do I look like your secretary?

21:43.444 --> 21:45.242
Yeah, it must be your lipstick.

21:45.446 --> 21:47.540
Hold on a second. Dale!

21:49.742 --> 21:51.502
- Jackson here.
TONY (OVER PHONE): <i>It's Tony.</i>

21:51.619 --> 21:52.836
Tony, I'm sorry. I...

21:53.037 --> 21:56.166
<i>Where have you been?
Come over as soon as you can.</i>

21:56.373 --> 21:57.875
<i>This is a matter of life and death.</i>

21:58.083 --> 21:59.926
(DIAL TONE)

22:04.214 --> 22:05.966
(TONY BREATHING HEAVILY)

22:13.057 --> 22:14.434
JACKSON: Hey, Tony?

22:15.267 --> 22:16.769
Tony.

22:20.481 --> 22:22.609
Jesus, Tony.
You don't look too good.

22:22.816 --> 22:24.489
How'd you get in here?

22:26.695 --> 22:28.163
It was open.

22:28.614 --> 22:29.661
(CHUCKLES)

22:29.823 --> 22:31.917
Hey, what happened? Who did this?

22:32.117 --> 22:33.164
I did.

22:34.370 --> 22:35.713
You can never be too careful.

22:36.372 --> 22:37.874
The walls...

22:39.333 --> 22:42.883
The walls have ears,
and all of that.

22:43.420 --> 22:48.768
- Come on, I wanna take you to a hospital.
- No! No, no.

22:49.134 --> 22:50.181
- Whoa.
- Sit down.

22:54.765 --> 22:57.143
You sit down and
you're gonna listen.

23:01.105 --> 23:02.732
All right.

23:03.565 --> 23:05.112
Just cool it.

23:07.903 --> 23:11.749
- Looks like you haven't slept in days.
- I can't afford to sleep.

23:11.949 --> 23:13.246
Norman dead...

23:13.450 --> 23:14.997
Grantham dead...

23:15.202 --> 23:16.579
Stringer dead.

23:18.205 --> 23:21.084
And Tony alive.
For now.

23:21.291 --> 23:23.669
- Right?
- Who'd wanna kill you, Tony?

23:29.133 --> 23:31.807
I'll give you three guesses,
and the first two...

23:32.011 --> 23:34.730
you forget about.
All right?

23:34.930 --> 23:36.273
Here's a little hint:

23:36.473 --> 23:39.852
"Hot. Hotter. Hottest."

23:42.479 --> 23:44.231
Peter Dellaplane.

23:49.278 --> 23:53.499
<i>(SINGING)
I'd like to tell you a story</i>

23:56.410 --> 24:01.337
<i>About a man and the many
