exactly like you at the time.

01:20:45.941 --> 01:20:48.114
(WHISPERS)
To most of my guests...

01:20:48.318 --> 01:20:50.366
you all look alike anyway.

01:20:52.489 --> 01:20:55.368
They'll assume you're
on a mission to kill me...

01:20:55.576 --> 01:20:58.125
after your senseless
murder of my wife.

01:20:58.328 --> 01:21:02.629
And the interesting thing is,
your getaway car will crash and burn.

01:21:02.833 --> 01:21:06.133
Your charred body will be discovered
among the ruins...

01:21:06.837 --> 01:21:09.932
and you'll be identified
from your dental records.

01:21:10.340 --> 01:21:13.935
And the case will be neatly closed.

01:21:14.136 --> 01:21:15.433
Immaculate.

01:21:16.054 --> 01:21:19.433
Thank you. Thank you very much.
I think so too.

01:21:20.100 --> 01:21:22.023
That only leaves Sydney.

01:21:22.853 --> 01:21:25.151
She will die of an overdose.

01:21:26.773 --> 01:21:29.868
But not until I fuck her
one last time.

01:21:30.068 --> 01:21:32.912
You really shouldn't wear
your heart on your sleeve.

01:21:33.113 --> 01:21:34.956
It's very unbecoming.

01:21:41.205 --> 01:21:43.333
What do you want from me,
Dellaplane?

01:21:44.124 --> 01:21:45.876
What do you want from me?

01:21:47.085 --> 01:21:49.634
I want you to die.

01:22:00.140 --> 01:22:01.608
JACKSON: Dellaplane.

01:22:01.808 --> 01:22:04.436
One of these days, you're
gonna really piss me off.

01:22:08.690 --> 01:22:13.287
Thaw, get the gasoline.
We're gonna have us a little barbecue.

01:22:18.158 --> 01:22:20.252
Tell me where it hurts.

01:22:30.337 --> 01:22:32.840
Hello, I'm Mr. Edd.

01:22:33.757 --> 01:22:35.350
You called about a paint job?

01:22:35.551 --> 01:22:36.803
(GRUNTING)

01:22:47.688 --> 01:22:49.531
(YELLING)

01:23:02.911 --> 01:23:04.333
Chill out.

01:23:07.499 --> 01:23:09.001
Shit!

01:23:14.840 --> 01:23:16.092
(GUNSHOT)

01:23:44.536 --> 01:23:45.583
Looking for me?

01:23:46.496 --> 01:23:48.089
(GRUNTS)

01:23:56.590 --> 01:23:57.716
Barbecue, huh?

01:23:58.842 --> 01:24:00.389
How do you like your ribs?

01:24:04.890 --> 01:24:06.642
(BAND PLAYING CLASSICAL MUSIC)

01:24:10.020 --> 01:24:12.022
(CHATTERING)

01:24:16.151 --> 01:24:17.903
Fine, thank you.

01:24:20.322 --> 01:24:22.791
Thank you.
Thank you very much.

01:24:33.794 --> 01:24:35.171
Thanks.

01:24:39.007 --> 01:24:40.429
Thank you, yeah.

01:24:44.471 --> 01:24:46.269
Why did you have to bring me?

01:24:46.473 --> 01:24:48.817
- You remind me of a friend.
- Why not bring him?

01:24:49.017 --> 01:24:50.109
He's dead.

01:24:51.436 --> 01:24:54.189
Damn, man. Why'd you
have to tell me that?

01:25:26.304 --> 01:25:27.977
KID: I recommend the crab cake.

01:25:30.058 --> 01:25:31.480
(EDD & KID CHUCKLE)

01:25:33.854 --> 01:25:37.654
Peter, I'm scandalized.
There was no one to park our car.

01:25:37.858 --> 01:25:39.860
I'm sorry. I'll see to it.

01:25:40.068 --> 01:25:43.072
- Please. Nice to see you.
- You look wonderful.

01:25:46.742 --> 01:25:51.248
Something's wrong.
I want you to check out front. Hustle.

01:25:57.335 --> 01:25:59.508
Ladies and gentlemen,
can I have your attention?

01:25:59.713 --> 01:26:02.762
Ladies and gentlemen!
Your attention, just for a moment.

01:26:03.383 --> 01:26:05.511
I want you to meet
our birthday boy...

01:26:06.094 --> 01:26:08.973
Raymond Foss! Ray, come on
up here and say a few words.

01:26:18.356 --> 01:26:20.074
Raymond Foss.

01:26:21.026 --> 01:26:22.448
- Run.
- Run?

01:26:22.652 --> 01:26:25.246
- Run!
- Excuse me, sir.

01:26:26.531 --> 01:26:28.533
I'm happy to see old
friends here...

01:26:28.742 --> 01:26:31.370
to celebrate my birthday with me.

01:26:31.578 --> 01:26:33.125
When a man gets to be my age...

01:26:33.330 --> 01:26:35.753
all that's left are old friends.

01:26:35.957 --> 01:26:37.379
(RAYMOND CHUCKLES)

01:26:38.001 --> 01:26:40.095
Really, this evening...

01:26:40.879 --> 01:26:43.132
is the happiest evening of my life.

01:26:43.340 --> 01:26:44.780
- Excuse me. Sorry, ma'am.
WOMAN: Ow!

01:26:44.883 --> 01:26:48.183
Looks like someone else is having
a good time out there. Ha, ha.

01:26:49.012 --> 01:26:53.313
Someone should tell that man
there's plenty of cake for everyone.

01:26:58.772 --> 01:27:01.025
(YELLING)

01:27:05.529 --> 01:27:07.076
(THUD)

01:27:09.866 --> 01:27:11.459
(GROANING)

01:27:16.873 --> 01:27:20.594
Dellaplane did it!
Dellaplane did it!

01:27:20.794 --> 01:27:21.920
He planned...

01:27:22.128 --> 01:27:23.175
(WOMAN SCREAMS)

01:27:24.923 --> 01:27:27.176
(GASPS)

01:27:28.760 --> 01:27:29.807
Get out of the way.

01:27:30.011 --> 01:27:32.264
Get the chopper.
I'll meet you there.

01:27:36.142 --> 01:27:37.485
Going someplace?

01:27:52.993 --> 01:27:54.711
Hey. You're Kid Sable, aren't you?

01:27:54.911 --> 01:27:56.959
You better believe it, brother.

01:27:57.539 --> 01:27:58.961
ALBERT: Excuse me, sir.

01:27:59.624 --> 01:28:00.967
(ALBERT GASPS)

01:28:04.129 --> 01:28:05.551
(GRUNTS)

01:28:07.340 --> 01:28:10.014
I hope this teaches you,
crime doesn't pay.

01:28:12.679 --> 01:28:13.726
Huh?

01:28:13.930 --> 01:28:15.432
KOTTERWELL: Jackson!

01:28:17.601 --> 01:28:19.353
Where do you think you're going?

01:28:19.561 --> 01:28:20.653
You gonna take me in?

01:28:20.854 --> 01:28:22.276
Any reason why I shouldn't?

01:28:24.900 --> 01:28:28.279
Jackson!
Jackson!

01:28:31.531 --> 01:28:34.125
- Fuck it.
JACKSON: Thanks.

01:28:40.165 --> 01:28:42.088
Easy, baby.

01:28:45.879 --> 01:28:47.051
Get out of the way!

01:28:49.382 --> 01:28:50.429
Get out of the way!

01:29:01.144 --> 01:29:02.737
You lose.

01:29:07.400 --> 01:29:08.492
Hot.

01:29:17.535 --> 01:29:18.661
Hotter.

01:29:26.044 --> 01:29:28.172
- Hottest!
- Christ!

01:29:41.935 --> 01:29:43.528
You haven't learned your lesson?

01:29:44.104 --> 01:29:45.481
Teach me.

01:29:51.820 --> 01:29:53.242
(SYDNEY WHIMPERING)

01:30:17.012 --> 01:30:18.639
SYDNEY: Just shoot him.

01:30:19.931 --> 01:30:23.481
Jackson, what are you doing?
Just shoot the son of a bitch.

01:30:28.565 --> 01:30:30.738
Jackson, what are you doing?

01:30:35.405 --> 01:30:37.282
Jackson, don't do it.

01:30:43.413 --> 01:30:44.835
(SIRENS WAILING IN DISTANCE)

01:31:11.232 --> 01:31:12.484
(YELLS)

01:31:14.194 --> 01:31:15.571
Now you pissed me off.

01:31:52.357 --> 01:31:54.826
- How did he miss?
- He didn't.

01:31:55.026 --> 01:31:56.073
Are you all right?

01:31:56.277 --> 01:31:57.529
Hell, no. I've been shot.

01:31:57.737 --> 01:31:59.159
ARMBRUSTER: Check him out.

01:31:59.906 --> 01:32:01.658
How bad is it?

01:32:01.866 --> 01:32:05.621
Oh. This is one dead
piece-of-shit car builder. Heh.

01:32:08.498 --> 01:32:11.672
I want the paramedics and a meat
wagon down here right away.

01:32:11.876 --> 01:32:14.755
I want a full report on my desk
first thing in the morning.

01:32:14.963 --> 01:32:18.934
- In the morning?
- In the morning, lieutenant.

01:32:20.009 --> 01:32:21.056
Lieutenant?

01:32:21.261 --> 01:32:24.356
- Lieutenant?
- Is there an echo around here?

01:32:26.683 --> 01:32:28.685
You always said you wouldn't team up
with a junkie.

01:32:28.893 --> 01:32:30.236
How about an ex-junkie, huh?

01:32:30.436 --> 01:32:32.029
Wait a minute. You kidding?

01:32:32.230 --> 01:32:36.235
Cold turkey. You can have me
on Thanksgiving. How's that?

01:32:37.485 --> 01:32:38.953
Can I have you any sooner?

01:32:39.154 --> 01:32:41.156
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

01:35:51.763 --> 01:35:53.765
(English - US - SDH)
